title: Need a solid duo partner
body:
I've been playing a shit ton lately and I'm just trying to find someone to duo with. Don't want toxic ppl and Add me if you're interested. I'm aiming to get to gold soon. Add me if you're interested.

Amenadiel

hi i play tons of lol (when ever i can) and Im looking for a duo partner
